nied in the final strides by the fast-finishing American Quincy Hall, who took gold by four-hundredths of a second in a rapid time of 43.40sec.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999995609492598, \"rank\": 3.2889312470826484e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999999998381099, \"rank\": 1.1894420627297412e-10, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"intolast night's 400m finalas\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest man\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"a first global title\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"the final strides\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"four-hundredths\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"a rapid time\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"43.40sec\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both men leaped into the top five on the all-time list, with Hudson-Smith shattering his own European record, but he was ultimately forced to settle for silver again, having also finished second in last year's world final in Budapest.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.445944466601687e-29, \"text\": \"European record\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999992041083244, \"rank\": 7.958921744740453e-07, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both men\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-time list\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought I had it,\\\" the Briton admitted.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Briton\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew coming in it would come down to the last 50 metres.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last 50 metres\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the last 50 came, he was strong and he nicked it.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's it.\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not angry, I am not upset.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's life at the end of the day.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1124}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will always only be one winner.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one winner\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[Hall] did what he had to do, he came on strong.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hall\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not complain.\\\"\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a decade since Hudson-Smith made his major breakthrough when breaking 45sec as a teenager, but his career since has been heavily disrupted by injury, as well as the mental health struggles that saw himattempt suicide in 2021.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decade\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"his major breakthrough\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"the mental health struggles\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"himattempt suicide\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At 29, though, the Birchfield Harrier is clearly in the form of his life and, crucially, still improving as he already sets his sights on Los Angeles in 2028 and an elusive gold medal.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birchfield_v._North_Dakota\", \"score\": 0.9999999955680323, \"rank\": 4.372638359367212e-09, \"text\": \"Birchfield\", \"types\": [\"Q2334719\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birchfield_v._North_Dakota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birchfield_v._North_Dakota\"}, {\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999951642167, \"rank\": 4.791819526161252e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been in the game a long time, but had a relatively short career,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"a relatively short career\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2015, I had stress fractures, 2016 was up and down, I tore my hamstring.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stress fractures\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"my hamstring\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2017, I had a lot of personal problems outside of the sport, 2018 I moved to America, 2019 I tore my Achilles... 2020 was Covid, 2021 - let us not even talk about it.\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 2016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999727152, \"rank\": 2.7102442266247357e-11, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"personal problems\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then, literally, about 2022 is when it really started to click.\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is just the start.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the start\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My time is going to come at the end of the day.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My time\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have another four years left and then I am out.\\\"\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another four years\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other than his conqueror, Hall, last night, only three men in history have run faster than Hudson-Smith's new personal best 43.44sec: American greats Butch Reynolds and Michael Johnson, and South Africa's world-record holder Wayde van Niekerk.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999995609492598, \"rank\": 3.2889312470826484e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2357, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butch_Reynolds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Butch Reynolds\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butch_Reynolds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Butch_Reynolds\"}, {\"begin\": 2376, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.2753288987434648, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\"}, {\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9974579604838045, \"rank\": 0.0025101477670819413, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2432, \"end\": 2449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wayde van Niekerk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his conqueror\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"Hall\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"only three men\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith's new personal best 43.44sec\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hudson-Smith finished eighth in the 2016 Olympic final in which Van Niekerk set that mark (43.03sec), and believes he can get close to, or possibly even better it before his career is done.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Olympic final\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"that mark\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"43.03sec\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the best in the world when I am healthy,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is just the start.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the start\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will lower the time [in the 400m] and go for a 19 second [in the 200m] and shake things up a bit more.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions Reset your wellbeing for the year ahead \\\"When it clicks, it is going to be special.\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3011}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3030}, {\"ngram\": \"your wellbeing\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in the world-record race, so I know what is like to be in a calibre race where everyone is crazy and talented.\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world-record race\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"a calibre race\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have plans on bigger times.\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3251}, {\"ngram\": \"bigger times\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not come in theOlympics, but I have another four years, and that is the last you are going to see of me.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"another four years\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am never coming on the track ever again [after that].\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am getting fat, man.\\\"\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fat, man\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere, Amber Anning lowered her personal best to ensure Britain will go into tomorrow's women's 400m final with outside medal hopes.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3522, \"end\": 3529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9992649309009051, \"rank\": 0.0007356097715953664, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amber Anning\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"outside medal\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anning, who has already won bronze in the mixed 4x400m relay at these Games, ran 49.47sec in her semi-final to qualify fourth-fastest for the final.\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anning\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3605}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed 4x400m relay\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"49.47sec\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have a lot of confidence going into Friday,\\\" said the 23-year-old.\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3762}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3776}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud that I have given myself a chance of a medal.\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That medal [in the mixed 4x400m relay] has given me so much motivation to win another one.\\\"\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mixed 4x400m relay\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"so much motivation\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\"